</LIST>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Daugh.</SPEAKER>
<P>This is very plain indeed.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Fa.</SPEAKER>
<P>Go back next to the Books of <HI>Mo&s;es;</HI> The Pro|phe&s;ies
