</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Fa.</SPEAKER>
<P>That is a particular Ca&s;e, wherein GOD ap|peared
to a wicked Man, magnifying his Power in
over-ruling what the <HI>Devil</HI> de&s;igned to do by his
Hand, and is an Argument to prove what I &s;ay,
