</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Daugh.</SPEAKER>
<P>What do you conclude from all this, Sir?</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Fa.</SPEAKER>
<P>I &s;ay all this confirms the Divine Authority
