it mu&s;t be then, that GOD alone has &s;poken in all
tho&s;e Prophe&s;ies, that the Scripture is dictated by
his immediate Spirit, and that it is really the Word
of GOD.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Daugh.</SPEAKER>
<P>It is an Argument indeed which I never
