&s;hould be betray'd to him; it is clear to me
then, that all the Scripture Prophe&s;ies are from
<HI>Heaven.</HI></P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Fa.</SPEAKER>
<P>All from <HI>Heaven,</HI> Child! all the Voice of
