</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Fa.</SPEAKER>
<P>Yes, it is, exactly.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Daugh.</SPEAKER>
<P>Be plea&s;ed, Sir, to give us &s;ome Exam|ples
