</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Son.</SPEAKER>
<P>That Text you quoted before, I think, &s;tates
both the Ca&s;es, 2 <HI>Phil.</HI> vi. it &s;ays expre&s;sly, <HI>Being
