</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Son.</SPEAKER>
<P>It is certainly for want of di&s;tingui&s;hing in
the&s;e particular Articles, and knowing when the
Scripture &s;peaks of him as GOD, and when as <HI>Me|diator,</HI>
