St. <HI>John</HI> &s;ays, <HI>He needed not that any &s;hould te&s;tify of
Men, for he knew what was in Man,</HI> John ii. 25.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Son.</SPEAKER>
<P>The Di&s;tinction runs through every Tran&s;|action
