with&s;tand the Force of it.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<PB N="333" REF="347">
<SPEAKER>Son.</SPEAKER>
<P>It would be endle&s;s indeed to reckon up all
the &s;everal Texts in the Scripture, which a&s;&s;ure
us of the Divinity of his Per&s;on; but this Way of
arguing from them is, in my Opinion, as convincing
