</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Fa.</SPEAKER>
<P>But &s;uppo&s;e we had, What can they &s;ay?
Could <HI>Je&s;us,</HI> as Man, &s;end the Holy Spirit of Truth
among Men? When the Holy Gho&s;t was &s;ent, and
<PB N="334" REF="348">
had de&s;cended upon them, then indeed they were
<HI>indued with Power from on high,</HI> &s;o that on whom|&s;oever
they laid Hands they received al&s;o the Holy
Gho&s;t; but the Di&s;ciples did not &s;end it: The
&s;ending the Holy Gho&s;t was certainly the immediate
