</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Fa.</SPEAKER>
<P>You may ob&s;erve our ble&s;&s;ed Lord is all
along called <HI>the Son of God,</HI> and he owns him&s;elf to
be &s;o; now he is properly and particularly the Son
of the Holy Gho&s;t, as is plain from the Account
