of him&s;elf, <HI>does nothing</HI> of him&s;elf, <HI>comes not</HI>
of him&s;elf, but is &s;ent by the Father, is le&s;s than the
Father, and does the Will of his Father, keeps his
Father's Commandments, <HI>and the like:</HI> All the&s;e are
